                     <interp inst="t17801206-7-off32" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17801206-7-off32" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a silver quart tankard, value 3 l. 10 s. and eight silver table spoons, value 3 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17801206-7-victim105" type="victimName">
                     George 
                     Hebden
                  <interp inst="t17801206-7-victim105" type="surname" value="Hebden"></interp>
